daveayan.gherkinsalad.components
Class NullBrowserElement

java.lang.Object
  daveayan.gherkinsalad.components.NullBrowserElement
All Implemented Interfaces:
BrowserElement, CanBeDisabled, CanBeEnabled, Clickable, Selectable, TextEnterable, Nullable
public class NullBrowserElement
extends Object
implements Clickable, Selectable, TextEnterable, BrowserElement

Implementing the Null Object Pattern this object is returned back if an element cannot be found on the browser. Calling any method on this class will result in an assertion error.
